## Add-on statistics
## These strings are used to display the total number of
## users and rating for an add-on. They are shown next to each other.

# Variables:
#   $total (Number) - The rating of the add-on from 1 to 5
cfr-doorhanger-extension-rating =
    .tooltiptext =
        { $total ->
              [one] { $total } stella
             *[other] { $total } stelle
        }
